data.message: Hey, shady I know that today is not your birthday, the is my birthday just want to say that it is mine, and thank you for being the artist that you are the person who you are no matter what others say to me you will be my thanks for shady rejoice with your music and crazy over the years want to tell you I love you unconditionally and waiting for the new jobs. I hope someday to attend a show yours. Thank you for everything.
